{"tid":54480,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"畀鱷魚咬iPhone 7 到底咬唔咬得爛？","createTime":"2016-12-25T14:32:48.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-25T15:19:27.000Z","uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"76e3fa46ab870d8e965eb0a63eb4b360e479e342","tid":54480,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T14:32:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20161225&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=56090689\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20161225%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D56090689&d=K0iBZ6rl8Rud6QRIZBRUzksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=05cc22a5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20161225%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D56090689&h=a10f090d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20161225&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=56090689</a><br />\n蘋果的iPhone 7被用家譽為歷來最堅硬的iPhone，美國加州一班科技迷質疑這個說法，並找來鱷魚測試其堅硬度。<br />\n從片段可見，一名科技迷拿金屬臂鉗着一部iPhone 7手機，把手機放到鱷魚嘴邊。起初鱷魚咬一口後又鬆開，似乎不太感興趣，第二次嘗試才咬住iPhone<br />\n眾人取回iPhone後，發現手機仍可以運作，但屏幕出現裂痕，底部外殼亦有牙齒印。<br />\n他們死心不息，再次把iPhone「餵」鱷魚。這次牠大力咬緊不放，iPhone最後當然報銷了，雖然機身未有折斷，屏幕亦有畫面，但已不能操作了<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6fqZ5CV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6fqZ5CV.jpg&h=77ce7a9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n用部note7試下有乜後果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71180ebf04cd2a58808c719cae95b8369fb97ed3","tid":54480,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T14:36:13.000Z","msg":"隻鱷魚會炸死"},{"pid":"19341ed37924d83230375e531f472e35a6d47874","tid":54480,"uid":39331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T14:37:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>隻鱷魚會炸死</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n鱷魚測試電話硬度被炸死 三星表示遺憾"},{"pid":"fa460e89a20d1b2fe6370a26bfbdf7344a70d470","tid":54480,"uid":19301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T14:37:40.